				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the media conglomerate.  For the television network, see <a href="ABS-CBN" title="ABS-CBN">ABS-CBN</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">Not to be confused with <a href="Akita_Broadcasting_System" title="Akita Broadcasting System">Akita Broadcasting System</a>.</div>
