<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=ABS-CBN_Corporation&action=edit&section=26.php.html" title="Edit section: Affiliates">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Affiliates">Affiliates</span></h3>
<p>Here is a list of companies that are affiliated with ABS-CBN. Note that the company (ABS-CBN) only holds economic interest to the following.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="AMCARA_Broadcasting_Network" title="AMCARA Broadcasting Network" class="mw-redirect">AMCARA Broadcasting Network</a> (49%)<sup id="cite_ref-owner_2-55" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-owner-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>Beyond Cable Holdings, Inc. (7%)<sup id="cite_ref-owner_2-56" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-owner-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>Sky Vision Corporation (18.8%)<sup id="cite_ref-owner_2-57" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-owner-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=ABS-CBN_Corporation&action=edit&section=27.php.html" title="Edit section: Non-stock organizations">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Non-stock_organizations">Non-stock organizations</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="ABS-CBN_Foundation,_Inc." title="ABS-CBN Foundation, Inc.">ABS-CBN Foundation, Inc.</a>- the umbrella organization of <a href="Bantay_Bata" title="Bantay Bata">Bantay Bata</a> (Child Watch), Bantay Baterya (Battery Watch), <a href="Bantay_Kalikasan" title="Bantay Kalikasan">Bantay Kalikasan</a> (Environmental Watch), BayaniJuan (Country of Juan), E-Media (Educational television), Kapit Bisig Para sa Ilog Pasig (Holding together for Pasig River), No to Mining in Palawan, and Sagip Kapamilya (Saving Members of the Family).</li>
<li>ABS-CBN Bayan Foundation, Inc.</li>
<li>71 Dreams Foundation, Inc.</li>
</ul>
